description: Returns a list of objects associated with a profile of a given ProfileObjectType.

parameters.name: DomainName
parameters.description: The unique name of the domain.

parameters.name: ObjectTypeName
parameters.description: The name of the profile object type.

parameters.name: ProfileId
parameters.description: The unique identifier of a customer profile.

parameters.name: ObjectFilter
parameters.description: Applies a filter to the response to include profile objects with the specified index values. A searchable identifier of a profile object. The predefined keys you can use to search for _asset include: _assetId, _assetName, and _serialNumber. The predefined keys you can use to search for _case include: _caseId. The predefined keys you can use to search for _order include: _orderId. A list of key values. (string) ---

nested_params.name: KeyName
nested_params.description: A searchable identifier of a profile object. The predefined keys you can use to search for _asset include: _assetId, _assetName, and _serialNumber. The predefined keys you can use to search for _case include: _caseId. The predefined keys you can use to search for _order include: _orderId.

nested_items.name: ObjectTypeName
nested_items.description: Specifies the kind of object being added to a profile, such as 'Salesforce-Account.'

nested_items.name: ProfileObjectUniqueKey
nested_items.description: The unique identifier of the ProfileObject generated by the service.

nested_items.name: Object
nested_items.description: A JSON representation of a ProfileObject that belongs to a profile.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token from the previous call to ListProfileObjects.
